    "en": {
      "title": "Two arrested with 4,000 liters of petrol",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two persons have been arrested in Puttalam Kalatti area for illegally transporting 4,000 liters of petrol.",
        "The suspects were arrested on the basis of a tip-off when they were transporting petrol in a lorry from Anamaduai to Puttalam.",
        "The police informed that the said petrol was stored in 20 cells and said that they will produce the suspects in Puttalam Magistrate Court."
      ],
